  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Clean water and bathrooms for 1,000 schoolchildren</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Children need to be nourished to thrive at school. Safe drinking water is essential to ensure children stay healthy and retain all the nutrients they can.   A recent assessment at the Entebbe UMEA primary school found that the water and sanitation systems at the school were insufficient, jeopardizing the children&apos;s access to safe water and their health. We need your support to build an effective water filtration and storage system and improve the latrines and changing rooms for girls.</narrative>
  </description>
